comments: Best TA I have experienced in Red Bird Country yet. I think he\'s the only TA that could not be overshadowed by Dr. Hassani\'s shadow of bad-assitude. Also he ALWAYS commented on how "appealing" i looked most days, which I think is some sort of teacher slang for "ready to learn!" Def. Take Him!
Best TA I\'ve ever had. I don\'t hate watching him write on the board either ;) bring him raspberries get a guaranteed A
